<p>
<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha"><g type="pc"/> svasti śrī <supplied reason="undefined"><g type="ddanda">.</g></supplied> vijayātbudhaya</hi> kaliyu<hi rend="grantha">ga<unclear>sam</unclear>vatsaram <num value="4646">4 <g type="numeral">1000</g> 6 <g type="numeral">100</g> 4 <g type="numeral">10</g> 6</num></hi> Itaṉmeṟ cellāniṉ
<lb n="2" break="no"/>ṟa pilavaṅka varu<hi rend="grantha">ṣam</hi> Āvaṇi-mātam <hi rend="grantha"><num value="26">2 <g type="numeral">10</g> 6</num>-<g type="pc"/> pūrvapakṣa</hi> ttu Ekāteciyu muttirāṭamuñ cuk
<lb n="3" break="no"/>kiṟavāramum peṟṟa nāḷ <hi rend="grantha">śrīma</hi> ṉ<hi rend="grantha">mahārājādhirāja rāja</hi> <unclear>pa</unclear>ra<hi rend="grantha">meśvara śrī</hi>vīra<hi rend="grantha">pra</hi> tāpa catāci
<lb n="4" break="no"/>va<hi rend="grantha">de</hi>va<hi rend="grantha">ma hārā</hi> yar <hi rend="grantha">pṛdhvirājya</hi> m paṇṇiyaruḷukaiyil Avar kāriyattukkuk kaṟttarāṉa taṇpo
<lb n="5" break="no"/>ṟuppaiyaṉukku muḷvāy cūḻnta kuṉṟattūrttuṟkañ cellum nāḷiṟ koṅkāṉa vīracoḻa
<lb n="6" break="no"/>maṇṭalattu vaṭapūvāṇiyanāṭṭut tāramaṅkalattu veḷḷāḻar nilaṅkiḻār ma<hi rend="grantha">sta</hi> kakuṭori ma
<lb n="7" break="no"/>kuṭacūṭāmaṇi vaṇṇattaṭukkum vāṭātamālaiyum <unclear>pu</unclear>likkoṭiyumuḷḷa vaṇaṅkāmuṭimutaliyār na
<lb n="8" break="no"/>lluṭaiappar koṭṭaimutaliyār Immaṭi kaṭṭimutaliyār Iṉṉāṭṭu rāmakūṭalukku O<unclear>pa</unclear>
<lb n="9" break="no"/>ppaiyaṉ tampi tippappaiyaṉaik koṇṭu pu<hi rend="grantha">ṇya</hi> kālattil kāverikkaraiyil tāraivāṟ<unclear>pi</unclear>
<lb n="10" break="no"/>ttu <hi rend="grantha">dharmmasā</hi> taṉa<supplied reason="omitted">t</supplied>tukkut taḷattuk karaṇikkar kaiyeḻuttum Eḻutiviccukkoṇṭu vaṇa
<lb n="11" break="no"/>ṅkāmuṭicamuttirameṉṉum nāmateyam paṇṇi Akkiṟāram viṭṭeṉ Ituk kellai kiḻa
<lb n="12" break="no"/>kku vaṇaṅkāmuṭicamuttira meṉṉuṅ kuḷa maṟitiyākavun teṟkup piḷḷākkavuṇṭaṉi<note n="11-1">Incomplete.</note>
</p>

